$ $ORACLE_HOME/rdbms/admin/catldr.sql

`catldr.sql` creates → development/databases/Oracle/objects/views[views] that are necessary for *direct path loads* in → development/databases/Oracle/tools/sql-loader.

These views are
  • `loader_tab_info`
  • `loader_part_info`
  • `loader_param_info`
  • `loader_constraint_info`
  • `loader_trigger_info`
  • `loader_file_ts`
  • `loader_ref_info`
  • `loader_oid_info`
  • `loader_dir_objs` (for which the synoym `datapump_dir_objs` is also created)
  • `loader_col_info`
  • `loader_col_flags`
  • `loader_lob_flags`
  • `loader_skip_unusable_indexes`
  • `loader_col_type`
  • `loader_nested_varrays`
  • `loader_full_attr_name`
  • `loader_intcol_info`
  • `loader_lob_index_tab`
  • `loader_lob_index_col`
  • `loader_db_open_read_write`
  • `gv$loadpstat`, `v$loadpstat`
  • `gv$loadistat`, `v$loadistat`
